Title: Coronavirus: New York sees glimmer of progress, New Orleans worsens - The Indian Express
Description: New York State as a whole, accounting for roughly half the country's known infections, followed California last week in ordering non-essential businesses to close and to direct residents to stay home as much as possible.

Title: Coronavirus cases in India rise to 606 | Death toll stand at 10 | COVID-19 - WION
Description: India has seen a huge rise in the number of coronavirus cases with the total number of confirmed cases now rising to 606. The death toll in the country stand...

Title: Coronavirus pandemic: Foreigner treated with HIV drugs for Covid-19 tests negative - India Today
Description: A British national, who had earlier tested positive for Covid-19, responded well to the drugs combination of Ritonavir and Lopinavir (HIV antiretroviral drugs), and his latest test results showed he has tested negative for the virus, a hospital statement said.

Title: British pensioners plead for Foreign Office rescue from Indian hospital quarantine - Telegraph.co.uk
Description: Five elderly British tourists being held in ‘extremely poor conditions’ in an Indian quarantine facility after testing positive for coronavirus have pleaded with the Foreign and Commonwealth Office (FCO) to do more to help them.
